overview: Nikita decides to surprise her husband by taking him to a Parisian apartment. He discovers that a young woman - Clara Mia - is waiting for them. Will he resist seeing his wife having fun with another woman without joining them? Never satisfied, Nikita will then play to increase the excitement to the maximum with Dorian and will organize a webcam in action or truth mode with girlfriends ... The icing on the cake? Nikita dressed in a vinyl bodysuit very close to the body, accompanied by her sex toys that she will stick from behind!
title: Obsessions 10
